Brenton M. DUNCAN, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D16-5278 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 15, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellant's motion to withdraw pleadings and the dismissal of this appeal filed on January 25, 2018 is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
